languages.text: "Слишком много пустоты. Кажется, будто в любой миг она оторвет тебя от земли и унесет в себя".
languages.translation_comment: Cassia: "It's absolutely vast! The sky above seems to stretch on and on. And all the spires below — hundreds and hundreds of them... So this is the Rogue Trader's palace!"

languages.text: "There is too much emptiness. It seems as if at any moment it will wrench you off the ground and pull you in."
